		"description": "<p>You have become exceptionally powerful from your mixing of artifice and traditional magical scholarship.&nbsp;You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Intelligence increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>Half of your Wizard levels count as Artificer levels for the purpose of determining your infusion limit.</li>\n<li>You can deactivate an infusion you have active during a short rest to gain an additional use of Arcane Recovery. When you deactivate an infusion this way, your infusion limit decreases by 1 until you finish a long rest.</li>\n<li>The costs (time and materials) for both scribing spells into your spellbook and creating spell inventions are halved.</li>\n</ul>",
